  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDocumentBase
    This interface should be implemented by the (sales order) document/header and is used for callbacks of the pricing engine.
    IExclusionCondition  
    IExternalDataSource
    The IExternalDataSource is an object which consists out of the elements conditionRate, pricingUnit and conditionBase in order to handle external data sources.
    IExternalPricingCondition  
    IExternalPricingConditions  
    IHeaderCondition
    A header condition is a pricing condition which has been typed in manually on the document level.
    IItemBase
    This interface should be implemented by the (sales order) item and is used for callbacks of the pricing engine.
    ILastPrice
    Interface for last price object.
    IPricingCondition
    A pricing condition contains information copied from the pricing knowledge base (from the customizing of the condition type and the pricing procedure), from the condition record, and from the result of the calculation.
    IPricingConditionCommon
    A pricing condition contains information copied from the pricing knowledge base (from the customizing of the condition type and the pricing procedure), from the condition record, and from the result of the calculation.
    IPricingConditionCurrencyConversionTraceResult  
    IPricingCurrencyConversionResult
    Represents the result of currency conversions in the pricing module.
    IPricingDocument
    The pricing document contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing items and provides methods which are processing all pricing items.
    IPricingDocument.ProcessMode  
    IPricingDocumentCommon
    The pricing document contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing items and provides methods which are processing all pricing items.
    IPricingDocumentObserver  
    IPricingEngine  
    IPricingItem
    The pricing item contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing conditions and provides methods which are working on all pricing condition of this pricing item.
    IPricingItemCommon
    The pricing item contains accumulated pricing information of all pricing conditions and provides methods which are working on all pricing condition of this pricing item.
    IPricingItemCommon.DynamicReturnContainerConstants
    This class defines all constants, which are used in the dynamic return container.
    IPricingItemCurrencyConversionTraceResult  
    IPricingProduct
    Interface to product master from the point of view of the Pricing Engine.
    IVariantCondition
    Interface for varcond-objects which can be created with the help of the pricing or conditionfinding engine.
